	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Encrypt and decrypt files using PGP/GPG.

Requirements:
- GPG installed via GPG Suite (https://gpgtools.org) or Homebrew: brew install gnupg
- At least one public key in your keyring for encryption

Usage:
- Encrypt: select any file in Alfred → Universal Actions → "Encrypt with PGP" → pick a recipient key
- Decrypt: select a .gpg/.pgp/.asc file → Universal Actions → "Decrypt with PGP"

Output files are placed next to the originals.
